snippet.title: Spikeout: Battle Street - Original Xbox Gameplay (2004)
snippet.description:
Spikeout: Battle Street - Original Xbox Gameplay (2004)

Subscribe: http://goo.gl/01dGfm

Spikeout: Battle Street (SPIKEOUT：バタル ストリート, Supaikauto: Bataru Sutorīto) is a beat 'em up video game for the Xbox home console. It was developed by Dimps and published by Sega, and is a successor to Sega's Spikeout series.




Recorded by Elgato Game Capture HD
